prisma_schema:
model ChatMessage {
  id              Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  text            String
  parentMessageId String?
  createdAt       DateTime @default(now())
  chatId          Int
  History         History  @relation(fields: [chatId], references: [id])
}

model History {
  id          Int           @id @default(autoincrement())
  title       String
  createdAt   DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime?
  ChatMessage ChatMessage[]
}

model Prompt {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  prompt    String
  title     String
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime?
}
